reviewText:
Good packaging, fast shipping, excellent product. Highly recommend.
Total Crack Up.
I don't buy things that I don't like or love!
VERY FUNNY FROM START TO FINISH! LOVE THE EXTRAS! ESPECIALLY THE INTERVIEWS! TOSH RULES! LOVE THAT ITS UNCENSORED! VERY GREAT BUY

Daniel tosh is a great comedian and his show is fantastic. I highly recommend this DVD to anyone who is a fan of comedy central, youtube videos or any of Daniel Tosh's stand up shows. This is a hilarious show worth owning.

If i had plenty of free time to kill alongside the rest of my normal hit list (looking at you patton oswalt), i would probably choose to pull out my pubes with a pair of tweezers instead of paying to watch this.
Tosh + DVD = funny and at a decent price.
Great buy but wish it was uncut
for the unedited stuff this is worth it... great buy.
We buy every season. DVD works perfectly. Product shipped fast.
Big  fan  of  Daniel  Tosh !!  Look  forward  to  future  seasons !
